scene.message:
Butterfly: I've been waiting.{waitkey}{clearbox}By saving the boy called Toro{nl}
from a Persona's power, the{nl}
Snow Queen's power has waned.{waitkey}{clearbox}The door sealed fast in ice{nl}
should open now.{waitkey}{clearbox}It is the entrance to one of{nl}
the three towers around the{nl}
school - the Tower of Hypnos.{waitkey}{clearbox}Of the three, this tower{nl}
has the simplest structure.{waitkey}{clearbox}The "Mirror Shards" should{nl}
be easy to find here.{waitkey}{clearbox}Oh, yes - let me give you{nl}
a warning about the towers.{waitkey}{clearbox}Once you set foot in any{nl}
tower, you cannot leave until{nl}
its master falls. Think first.{waitkey}{ret}

Butterfly: Welcome.{nl}
This is the entrance to the{nl}
Tower of Hypnos.{waitkey}{clearbox}Of the three, this tower{nl}
has the simplest structure.{waitkey}{clearbox}The "Mirror Shards" should{nl}
be easy to find here.{waitkey}{clearbox}Once you set foot in any{nl}
tower, you cannot leave until{nl}
its master falls. Think first.{waitkey}{ret}

Butterfly: Back again?{nl}
This is the entrance to the{nl}
Tower of Hypnos.{waitkey}{clearbox}Even now its master is gone,{nl}
demons still swarm within.{waitkey}{ret}

A sweet, drowsy scent{nl}
drifts from beyond the door.{waitkey}{clearbox}The door is frozen solid{nl}
and won't budge.{waitkey}{ret}

Tadashi: Wh-what's the big{nl}
deal? A little's fine, right?{nl}
You miser miser miser!{waitkey}{clearbox}Ah, no - I was talking to{nl}
this nagging girl here.{waitkey}{ret}

Tadashi: Two people can have{nl}
the same dream at the same{nl}
time, huh.{waitkey}{clearbox}This is no coincidence!{nl}
We were fated to be together.{waitkey}{ret}

Tadashi: I can see myself{nl}
in your eyes...{waitkey}{clearbox}Ahh, it's just getting good -{nl}
don't interrupt.{waitkey}{ret}

{color:2}Tadashi, a lazy member of{nl}
the fencing club. Fights with{nl}
Tamaki every day.{color:0}{waitkey}{ret}

Tamaki: He's terrible,{nl}
that Tadashi!{waitkey}{clearbox}The sports drinks I told him{nl}
not to drink on his own{nl}
'cause they're for everyone{waitkey}{clearbox}- he drank them ALL!!{waitkey}{ret}

Tamaki: I had a lovely dream{nl}
and realized my true{nl}
feelings.{waitkey}{clearbox}From now on...{nl}
I'll follow Tadashi.♥{waitkey}{ret}

Tamaki: Just being by his{nl}
side like this makes{nl}
me happy.♥{waitkey}{ret}

{color:3}Tamaki, a transfer student{nl}
in the fencing club. Fights{nl}
with Tadashi every day.{color:0}{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Fighting again.{nl}
Those two never get tired{nl}
of it, huh.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Tamaki's pretty cute.{nl}
Maybe Ayase should go{nl}
short too.♥{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Lucky, lucky~{nl}
Two young things warming{nl}
each other in a cold{nl}
room... so flavonoid~{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: This cold makes me{nl}
drowsy somehow...{nl}
No, no.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Lucky Tadashi,{nl}
got himself someone to{nl}
fight with.{waitkey}{clearbox}Being single is rough...{nl}
Ooh, cold~{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: "The Tower of Hypnos."{nl}
Hypnos is the god of sleep.{nl}
It doesn't seem too scary.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: What Ayase means -{nl}
could it be...{nl}
Platonic love?{waitkey}{clearbox}If she's doing it on purpose,{nl}
the wordplay's a bit much.{waitkey}Perhaps she means{nl}
"refreshing"?{waitkey}{ret}
